OL,3,CNotting Hill Carnival fugitive jailed
OL,4,Cfor bus driver's stab murder
OL,6,FA fugitive has been jailed for
OL,7,Fmurdering his ex-girlfriend's father
OL,8,Fafter being caught at Notting Hill
OL,9,FCarnival.
OL,11,FKamar Williams, 34, was sentenced to
OL,12,Flife imprisonment with a minimum term
OL,13,Fof 29 years at the Old Bailey on
OL,14,FFriday for stabbing bus driver Derek
OL,15,FThomas, 55, in Hackney, north-east
OL,16,FLondon, last July 30.
OL,18,FAfter the "frenzied" attack, Williams,
OL,19,Ffrom the Isle of Dogs, east London,
OL,20,Fwent on the run for a month, the court
OL,21,Fheard.
