OL,6,FHe was finally detained at Notting
OL,7,FHill Carnival last August 26, having
OL,8,Favoided police in a car chase last
OL,9,FAugust 3.
OL,11,FHer Honour Judge Angela Rafferty KC
OL,12,Ftold Williams that he had targeted Mr
OL,13,FThomas for "revenge because of your
OL,14,Fown fury", adding that the attack
OL,15,Finvolved "savage violence".
OL,17,FGiving her sentencing remarks, Judge
OL,18,FRafferty said: "I am sure that you
OL,19,Fintended to kill Derek Thomas. This
OL,20,Fwas a merciless and determined attack.
