OL,6,F"You killed him even though at one
OL,7,Ftime you saw him as a father figure.
OL,9,F"You knew how important he was to his
OL,10,Fwife and his children as you had lived
OL,11,Falongside them for two years."
OL,13,FJudge Rafferty added: "On July 30 last
OL,14,Fyear, you were simmering with rage
OL,15,Fthroughout the evening having been
OL,16,Farguing with your ex-partner Carron
OL,17,FThomas and her family.
