OL,6,F"I am sure that in your frustration
OL,7,Fand anger, you planned to have a
OL,8,Fviolent confrontation with one of the
OL,9,FThomas family that night.
OL,11,F"Mr Thomas died there on the street
OL,12,Fminutes from his home with the
OL,13,Fshopping he had bought strewn around
OL,14,Fhim."
OL,16,FJurors had been told the defendant had
OL,17,Fbeen looking for the victim's daughter
OL,18,FCarron Thomas on the night of the
OL,19,Fmurder.
