OL,6,FThe jury heard that Ms Thomas had
OL,7,Fcalled police twice in the hours
OL,8,Fbefore her father was attacked.
OL,10,FJust before 7pm, she reported to
OL,11,Fpolice that Williams was at her
OL,12,Fsister's address, but when police
OL,13,Farrived he was not there.
OL,15,FThen just after 10.30pm, she called
OL,16,Fpolice again, while she was at her
OL,17,Fsister's house, believing she could
OL,18,Fsee Williams walking through the
OL,19,Festate.
