OL,6,FWilliams went to Mr Thomas's home
OL,7,Flooking for him or his daughter, but
OL,8,Fthey were not in.
OL,10,FAs he was driving away, he spotted Mr
OL,11,FThomas walking home on Stoke Newington
OL,12,FCommon at around 11pm.
OL,14,FMr Thomas, who had been married for 35
OL,15,Fyears, had finished a late shift as a
OL,16,Fbus driver and gone into Tesco for
OL,17,Fsome food before heading home.
