OL,6,FWilliams stopped the van he was
OL,7,Fdriving in the middle of the road, got
OL,8,Fout and stabbed the grandfather five
OL,9,Ftimes.
OL,11,FMs Thomas said her father was a "kind,
OL,12,Fgentle and loving man" who "did not
OL,13,Fdeserve to have his life taken in such
OL,14,Fa senseless way".
OL,16,FIn a victim impact statement that was
OL,17,Fread to the court, Ms Thomas said:
OL,18,F"What makes this loss even more
OL,19,Fpainful is that the person responsible
OL,20,Fis someone I shared a relationship
OL,21,Fwith.
