OL,6,F"My family is broken. We are trying to
OL,7,Fcarry on, but we do so with heavy
OL,8,Fhearts, we feel our father's absence
OL,9,Fin every moment."
OL,11,FMr Thomas's sister, Blondelle Thomas,
OL,12,Fsaid her brother was a "dedicated bus
OL,13,Fdriver" with Go Ahead London and had
OL,14,Fbeen a "prolific footballer who
OL,15,Fretired early due to injury".
