OL,6,FReading her victim impact statement at
OL,7,Fthe sentencing, Ms Thomas added: "My
OL,8,Fbrother Derek Thomas was cruelly and
OL,9,Fbrutally ripped away from me and all
OL,10,Fwho loved and cared about him on July
OL,11,F30 2024.
OL,13,F"I cannot hold my brother, I'll never
OL,14,Fhear his words 'I love you sister'
OL,15,Fagain.
OL,17,F"I'm truly grateful to have had
OL,18,FDerek's love and trust in my life."
